item.title: Welcome to try
item.description: #memes #socially_awkward_awesome_penguin Part of my family is hard core MAGAs. And they won’t shut up about it. So I answered every single shit they would say that was pro maga. Seems I hurt my sister’s feeling to the point that apparently she feels I isolated her and now is looking for psychological help. It was bad at my childhood home guys. The amount of bloody lips, bruises and scars. Hell he chocked me twice. And he still don’t want to admit that what he did was abuse. So now he’s frustrated that mean old me is answering back to ever racism comment my racist family says. So he goes to what used to work for him. Bully the fck out of me and try to intimate me. Today was the first time I was able to say fck you dad and I fucking dare you to lay a hand on me. I’m so fucking angry. Grammar mistakes. Sorry I rage wrote this. Hi. Thanks for all the kind words. To clarify I’m a woman and 34 years old. Yea it took me this long to finally stand up to him. But I don’t mean to get into a physical altercation with him. My dad is pretty built for his age. One punch from would cause some serious damage while one from me would be like a fish tail slapping your face. And im not depending on my hubby as well (even if he would love to have a go at him). It’s really me telling him that he can no longer touch me and if does I am pressing charges against him this time. I got into social work because of him. It was my way of fighting back but I still didn’t have the confidence to even tell him what he did was wrong.

“Let us think the unthinkable, let us do the undoable, let us prepare to grapple with the ineffable itself, and see if we may not eff it after all.” - Douglas Adams I try to keep my posts "good vibe zones". So, instead of finding the one thing in here you don't like and commenting only on that, also comment about something you DID like. Balance the negativity. Love you long time. So, I made a discord server. It's a relaxed environment where you can take/donate memes to the cause, play trivia twice a week, chat about lots of topics or about nothing at all. We also have Jack Box game night and are setting up movie night! Very laid back/relaxed vibe. Come hang with us. https://discord.gg/AWFV7FT3RQ I'm also on the imgcat server for updates & fun: https://discord.gg/TpjD37jgJ9 ***Also if you miss abbiistabbii's discord community good news!
